section.def:
Authority
                (訓練局) means the Clothing Industry Training
            Authority established by section 4;

chairman
                (主席) means the chairman of the Authority
            appointed under section 8;

export
                (出口) means to take, or cause to be taken, out of
            Hong Kong any clothing item;

exporter
                (出口商) means a person who exports clothing
            items;

levy
                (徵款)
            means the clothing industry training levy prescribed under section 22;

manufactured
                (製造), in relation to a clothing item, includes
            any process involved in the manufacture of the item;

member
                (委員) means a member of the Authority appointed
            under section 7;

paragraph.content:
consist solely of and are marked clearly as samples of clothing items and which
                the Commissioner is satisfied are intended to be distributed free of charge for the
                purpose of advertising such clothing items;

section.def:
transmit (傳送), in
            relation to any information, includes send, deliver, give, lodge, submit and furnish the
            information;

subsection.def:
*gazettal date (刊憲日期) means the date on which the Import and Export (Amendment)
                Ordinance 2025 (30 of 2025) is published in the
                Gazette;
